631,"uid":15572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T10:45:42.000Z","msg":"香港醫療資源緊絀，醫護人員又辛苦，好多都做到盲目晒，冇咁落力/做錯事都唔出奇。btw 如果唔係流晒血，明顯好嚴重果d傷者/病人，跟車d救護員係慢慢黎，完全唔急，拖好耐先送院，利申親身經歷。"},{"pid":"ed32b160d5d398042ce04c33686d427e95df8914","tid":183631,"uid":29008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T10:50:23.000Z","msg":"靠公立醫院就自求多福啦"},{"pid":"4d673f33295c5d21a9dcbbe3ccabaa01d7cf5441","tid":183631,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T10:51:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cd9664e92ac179e7c760e7a9c1ba1902cddc41e1","tid":183631,"uid":59526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T10:56:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港醫療資源緊絀，醫護人員又辛苦，好多都做到盲目晒，冇咁落力/做錯事都唔出奇。btw 如果唔係流晒血，明顯好嚴重果d傷者/病人，跟車d救護員係慢慢黎，完全唔急，拖好耐先送院，利申親身經歷。</blockquote><br />\n救護車唔係的士 救護員會做完 treatment 先開車 因為一開左車就咩都做唔到"},{"pid":"d104971262949ceb74ddec9510ab8004a1a54fc3","tid":183631,"uid":14298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T10:58:07.000Z","msg":"依加d菌愈黎愈勁 醫護人員都唔知會咁勁<br />\n醫唔返就賴落d醫護人員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n咩都有風險 無人可以100%肯定醫得返 <br />\n只可以話個死者唔好彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c5e1ec9419e7a30d77a0c93cdf4579d86e8a128","tid":183631,"uid":5739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T10:59:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>依加d菌愈黎愈勁 醫護人員都唔知會咁勁<br />\n醫唔返就賴落d醫護人員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n咩都有風險 無人可以100%肯定醫得返 <br />\n只可以話個死者唔好彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係 未檢查只可以開啲大包圍既藥<br />\n又要空肚 又要等再檢查好多野先知道咩事<br />\n等得黎已經惡化左"},{"pid":"94c86eb94b3e95011b201f483d8255518fc43346","tid":183631,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T11:06:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港醫療資源緊絀，醫護人員又辛苦，好多都做到盲目曬，冇咁落力/做錯事都唔出奇。btw 如果唔係流曬血，明顯好嚴重果d傷者/病人，跟車d救護員係慢慢黎，完全唔急，拖好耐先送院，利申親身經歷。</blockquote><br />\n5毛唔回醫療資源緊絀我回你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n資源少 --&gt; 醫護人員供不應求<br />\n距離 塞紅包先有得早D有得醫／密D過黎睇 + 乜都打點滴 日子不遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a22c43342ac0ce0da0c4e982c2ff420821b49a52","tid":183631,"uid":33970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T11:21:23.000Z","msg":"不過心臟出現急症唔應該用藥救命先，之後先諗咩問題咩？<br />\n如果仲慢慢諗問題，個病人唔會因為咁就釘左？<br />\n就算用完藥釘左，都唔關醫生事啊，病人命該如此，起碼醫生都在早期積極救治過，而唔係由得佢到最後一刻先救唔返。"},{"pid":"63b3ae0c99a0925240c4e2a0a91a5d83d475be65","tid":183631,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T11:23:09.000Z","msg":"器官衰竭可唔可以捐器官架？"},{"pid":"c301157709d0929528fc1c5420f5a2e97c0fae05","tid":183631,"uid":36964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T11:24:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>器官衰竭可唔可以捐器官架？</blockquote><br />\n講就易"},{"pid":"0db4115e468325dc127917a4eb1a6b6655c00179","tid":183631,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T11:27:09.000Z","msg":"講到入醫院就寫包單一定醫得好咁"},{"pid":"82acdf99d363cd079475bed1847dabf95d653304","tid":183631,"uid":27008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T11:28:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不過心臟出現急症唔應該用藥救命先，之後先諗咩問題咩？<br />\n如果仲慢慢諗問題，個病人唔會因為咁就釘左？<br />\n就算用完藥釘左，都唔關醫生事啊，病人命該如此，起碼醫生都在早期積極救治過，而唔係由得佢到最後一刻先救唔返。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你都戇鳩<br />\n解釋都廢撚事 <br />\n藥藥藥 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  食撚晒所有藥好無？"},{"pid":"97dea1fd6c882f781ab72d890fe8fec6e8deb3a0","tid":183631,"uid":5739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T11:30:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不過心臟出現急症唔應該用藥救命先，之後先諗咩問題咩？<br />\n如果仲慢慢諗問題，個病人唔會因為咁就釘左？<br />\n就算用完藥釘左，都唔關醫生事啊，病人命該如此，起碼醫生都在早期積極救治過，而唔係由得佢到最後一刻先救唔返。</blockquote><br />\n見佢話開頭維生指數正常<br />\n所以應該搵下個cause先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e9c71e7f0bd364cc8b2d0f5548abe308b90b434","tid":183631,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T11:31:16.000Z","msg":"早上只係嘔吐 夜晚就icy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b960d249b56e2e18323931cb5cbb486a67f9c0a","tid":183631,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T11:31:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>早上只係嘔吐 夜晚就icu <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"b7286071455291ac01557fd19d53338861837656","tid":183631,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T11:31:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ab0df4b9b827e2b92a78b540a125ff1c4465e817","tid":183631,"uid":54183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T11:31:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"524f91bd8b8349090019b3369996fd1862871f5e","tid":183631,"uid":52182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T11:32:43.000Z","msg":"MI靠瀨抗生素做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a6e598979799aae77f8f1ed4fe7687a51460e1a","tid":183631,"uid":5739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T11:35:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>MI靠瀨抗生素做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n驗血報告發現，病人白血球指數及心臟肌鈣蛋白等數值異常，病人亦出現昏亂情況。<br />\n<br />\n醫生其後臨床診斷病人可能心肌炎及細菌感染，病人的情況也持續惡化，最終於同月26日死亡。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=216354&amp;home=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D216354%26home%3D1&d=BfE6afXCHr80cM3PNjd%2Fpy7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=7a5aaa69\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D216354%26home%3D1&h=fd700184\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=216354&amp;home=1</a>"},{"pid":"fb1ee65ee4b526cd1783d7b8b4811a25c843c498","tid":183631,"uid":20973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T11:39:40.000Z","msg":"佢唔好彩<br />\nMyocarditis<br />\n差得快"},{"pid":"8e43086e5a0b3e8fac2d25229f910de38964b450","tid":183631,"uid":33970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T11:41:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>不過心臟出現急症唔應該用藥救命先，之後先諗咩問題咩？<br />\n如果仲慢慢諗問題，個病人唔會因為咁就釘左？<br />\n就算用完藥釘左，都唔關醫生事啊，病人命該如此，起碼醫生都在早期積極救治過，而唔係由得佢到最後一刻先救唔返。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你都戇鳩<br />\n解釋都廢撚事 <br />\n藥藥藥 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  食撚晒所有藥好無？</blockquote><br />\n啱啱查左啲資料話第一時間要用利尿藥，唔知有冇錯，請巴打指教"},{"pid":"f3027c49fa998609073baad56cc184fe889d6611","tid":183631,"uid":53102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T11:54:22.000Z","msg":"Viral myocarditis<br />\n用antibiotic 幾快都無用啦<br />\n都係得supportive treatment <br />\nMortality 根本好高"},{"pid":"69c4b70b1438c8c25a0b2a1b5d6759fb4b3ab52d","tid":183631,"uid":24961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T11:56:44.000Z","msg":"啲家屬乜鳩都屌左醫護人員先 越黎越似大陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91087e8caa67af3ac77c19aea98d3f83a3e5adb7","tid":183631,"uid":5739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T11:57:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Viral myocarditis<br />\n用antibiotic 幾快都無用啦<br />\n都係得supportive treatment <br />\nMortality 根本好高</blockquote><br />\n好多人都覺得食藥/做手術先=treatment<br />\n檢查 抽血 留野化驗果啲做完冇好轉既就唔算"},{"pid":"76c8efaebfc582f1fd92261d8164802e3b19a47a","tid":183631,"uid":5739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-0