\n就算用完藥釘左，都唔關醫生事啊，病人命該如此，起碼醫生都在早期積極救治過，而唔係由得佢到最後一刻先救唔返。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你都戇鳩<br />\n解釋都廢撚事 <br />\n藥藥藥 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  食撚晒所有藥好無？</blockquote><br />\n啱啱查左啲資料話第一時間要用利尿藥，唔知有冇錯，請巴打指教</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n就算用完藥釘左，都唔關醫生事啊 &lt;- 你依個概念錯得好緊要<br />\n<br />\n同埋佢一入院維生指數正常，安排左驗呢樣果樣 ，要時間先出到result<br />\n<br />\n係乜都唔知+維生指數正常既情況之下  不如由你教醫生開咩藥好?<br />\n<br />\n送院22小時後才注射第一劑抗生素 ，都未至於好離譜 ，你估醫院剩係得你一個病人一個急症咩 <br />\n<br />\nBTW MI 導致Heart failure，雖然你的確可以話利尿藥對Heart failure有幫助，但唔等於佢醫到MI"},{"pid":"c15836ca1dd9138e189b3356d30ce81ef51a374e","tid":183631,"uid":27008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T12:55:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Viral myocarditis<br />\n用antibiotic 幾快都無用啦<br />\n都係得supportive treatment <br />\nMortality 根本好高</blockquote><br />\n邊到講viral?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n後生仔中myocarditis其實都預左... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c959a4b6e1b86fb8f082f823db9a94af65d3efe5","tid":183631,"uid":42767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T13:05:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>MI靠瀨抗生素做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n驗血報告發現，病人白血球指數及心臟肌鈣蛋白等數值異常，病人亦出現昏亂情況。<br />\n<br />\n醫生其後臨床診斷病人可能心肌炎及細菌感染，病人的情況也持續惡化，最終於同月26日死亡。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=216354&amp;home=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D216354%26home%3D1&d=BfE6afXCHr80cM3PNjd%2Fpy7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=7a5aaa69\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D216354%26home%3D1&h=fd700184\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=216354&amp;home=1</a></blockquot